errors.error_description: In the 'General Setup' code block, `import trax.fastmath` is called before `!pip install -q -U trax`, which will cause an `ImportError` because the module is used before it is installed.
correction_candidates: Move `import trax.fastmath` to after the `!pip install` command.
Replace the entire setup block with a single line: `!pip install -q -U trax && import trax`
